      "question": "The table below shows the exchange rate between the U.S. dollar and the Japanese yen on two dates.\n\n| Date       | Exchange Rate        |\n|------------|----------------------|\n| January 1  | 1 USD = 110 JPY      |\n| June 1     | 1 USD = 130 JPY      |\n\nBased on this information, which of the following most accurately describes the change and its most likely effect on U.S. trade with Japan?",
